terraform show
terraform validate
terraform refresh    --> to refresh the tfstate file


terraform fmt -write=false -diff output.tf  --> to show the incorrect formatting without a chage in the original file(particularly on output.tf file alone)
terraform fmt -diff  --> this will change the orginal files and show the output in terminal
terraform fmt --> this will also change but will not show the output in terminal

var command in variable file
terraform output --> this command will give us the output alone from statefile

